SP.P:
Very, very well, if I dye in thy debt for this crack∣rope)
let me be buried in a cole-sacke, I'le fit yee, (apes face)
looke for't.

Passing neat and exquisite, I protest faire creatures;
These honours to our solemnity, are liberall and uncommon;
my spouse and my selfe with our posterity, shall prostitute
our services, to your bounties, shals not duckling?

Here's a chaire, a chaire politique, my fine boy,
sit thee downe in triumph, and rise one of the nine Wor∣thies;
thou'lt be a sweet youth anon sirrah.

Confesse, or I shall marre your grace in whissing
Tobacco or squirting of sweet wines downe your gullet;
—you have beene offering to play the gelding we told
yee of I suppose;—speake truth, (move the semicircle of
your countenance to my left hand file) out with the truth;
would you have had a leap.
